<br>
This means, that as a Shadow Knight, your best use of taunt would be to hit the button when you believe you have lost taunt and then to follow up with a large hate producing spell.  If successful you'll now be at the top of the list plus the hate generated by your spell, usually more than enough to keep you there if no one else is being ridiculous.  If taunt fails, your aggro spells may still put you at the top of the list anyway.<br>
<br>
Taunt first, cast second. <p>The Man in Black: We are men of action, lies do not become us. <br>
